Ryan McGinnis <digicana@gmail.com>

[If previous reports from east China are to be relied upon, no illness or mortality will be seen in the migratory birds. To trace infection with H7N9, either the virus or antibodies against it should be discovered. Sampling could address organs, excrement and/or sera of migratory birds. - Mod.AS]

